\section TrackedImageIntro Introduction

The Tracked Image View plugin transforms an image plane so that it can be aligned with a moving tracker in a virtual scene. Figure 1 shows a rendering scene of a virtual ultrasound image plane aligned with a ultrasound probe.

\image html us_tracedimage_screenshot.png "Figure 1. A virtual ultrasound image aligned with a moving ultrasound probe (which has tag tracker attached)."

