\image html usage_1.png "Figure 2. The input from the plugin."

<ul>
<li> <b>image</b> Choose an image node to be rendered on the image plane. 
The image node is a data source tracked by the tracker.
</li>

<li> <b>image to world</b> Choose the transformation from model to world. </li>

<li> <b>do update</b> This check box allows the scene update in real-time when it is checked.</li>

</ul>
</ul>

<ul>
