\image html preferences_1.png "Figure 3. Set the plugin preferences."

<ul>

<li> <b>calibration matrix file name</b> Calibration matrix (4x4) from image plane to tracker.</li>

<li> <b>scaling in x direction</b> The scale factor obtained at the calibration stage.</li>

<li> <b>scaling in y direction</b> The scale factor obtained at the calibration stage.</li>

</ul>
</ul>

